Package models

package models
The models package contains classes that represent the fundamental building blocks of the application.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Account
    The Account class represents a user account in the system.
    Admin
    Represents an administrator in the system.
    Branch
    Represents a branch of the fast food chain, including details about the branch's name, location, and staff quota.
    BranchMenuItem
    Represents a menu item specific to a branch in a restaurant.
    BranchUser
    Represents a branch user in the system.
    Cart
    The Cart class represents a shopping cart that holds a collection of order items.
    Order
    Represents an order in the system.
    OrderItem
    Represents an item in an order.
    PaymentMethod
    The PaymentMethod class represents a payment method with its associated type.
    User
    This abstract class represents a generic user in the system.
